to opoio kanei compile kai link to arxeio ask2.c

Dokimh:
To programma dokimazetai me thn xrhsh tou "run_test.sh" to opoio
exei 3 diaforetika test:
1. 2 workers me input 2^31 - 1 2 fores kai meta mikroteroi arithmoi
2. 4 workers me input 2^31 - 1 2 fores kai oso oi prwtoi dyo einai blocked
dokimh mikroterwn arithmwn gia na doume pou anateithetai h douleia
3. 4 workers me 50 tyxaia inputs